...a stone chamber which reminded me of my old neighbors. Of course, that was a long time ago now, but would you believe their descendants are still telling stories about me and my family to their children?<br>
<br>
Even if most of the stories are lies and exaggerations, it is immortality of a sort.<br>
<br>
As I passed in front of an open doorway a figure, crossing the hall outside, saw me and immediately ran off.<br>
<br>
"Who was that?" they asked.<br>
<br>
"Another visitor, to be sure."<br>
<br>
"Why did he run away?"<br>
<br>
"You probably scared him," I said, and they apparently believed me.<br>
<br>
With few regrets on my part we left for...<br>
